{"type": "article", "id": 46067, "title": "上海时装周看这里，以及，LV和昆斯合作的包还是难看 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-10-13T03:45:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 121, "name": "Jeff Koons"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 2488, "name": "J.Crew"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 9781, "name": "周冬雨"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171013094714Qzg5P7v6GLcMDlwU.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/j-crew-founder-arthur-cinader-dead-at-11026513/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>J.Crew 创始人离世，享年 90 岁 </strong></a>| 周四上午，美国服饰品牌 J.Crew 的创始人 Arthur Cinader 离世，享年 90 岁。J.Crew 创办于 1983 年，1990 年销售额达到 4 亿美元。1997 年，Arthur Cinader 决定退休，J.Crew 的大多数股权被他以 5.6 亿美元的价格出售给了 TPG 德克萨斯太平洋集团。J.Crew 旗下还拥有年轻品牌 Madewell。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/493553\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>优衣库净利润大涨 150%</strong></a> | 截止至 8 月底，优衣库在今年的销售额增长了 4.2%，至 1.86 万亿日元，受中国及东南亚地区业绩的助推，优衣库的海外事业上涨了 8.2%，达 7081 亿日元。期内净利润大涨 150%，至 1192 亿日元。</p><p><b>周冬雨出任 Burberry 品牌形象大使</b> | 昨日，Burberry 通过官方微博宣布，周冬雨出任品牌形象大使，并曝光了一组周冬雨在伦敦拍摄的大片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013113257jlhITrnEWPZgA73M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>10 月 27 日，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/493437\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 和纽约艺术家 Jeff Koons 合作的第二个系列</a>即将上架。 </p><p>和第一波单品类似，这次的合作依然把 Jeff Koons 重现的原作画家本人的名字，马奈、高更、布歇等，写在包包上作为装饰，灵感来自《睡莲》与《草地上的午餐》等作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112117CKFu1cR4M3gpvTrN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112117jyt4pduKkASMTi6n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.689167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112116h0wJlbIcOHNyiRfW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.183750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112116KCBZ1usz9mw7HpMa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.181250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112117Lmvlrib5Y3eqfPSh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.273750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Tommy Hilfiger 发布 2017 秋季 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/tommy-hilfiger-fall-2017-capsule-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tommy Jeans 系列</a>，还找来了 Elliot Brown 和德国女演员 Zsa Zsa InciBürkle 拍摄 lookbook。该系列通过大胆用色和抢眼 logo、国旗等元素，试图找回 90 年代的美式复古休闲感。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101311214825EL6rszpuaD8XGv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112148dXQUS1rekgaTblEO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112149u8kDBEbG1JH9isc5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112150V8pqtkNSWK023xoa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131121507NoxELXW3Tezm6pO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112151ZvwyeGuiD6HkEjpA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112151fQ2zSriDk9VL5wmg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112152rmKgUYwI4dLfQFic.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112152QWZ9SmNjUFcb2PXo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112152uPIonp43SU1lOszv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112153zT6NWlwKUeXvESqx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112153JSc9IUrKevoAtF3g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上海时装周第一天，年轻设计师的主场 Labelhood 以“UNEXPECTED BELONGINGNESS 共鸣”为主题正式开启。 </p><p>WMWM 2018SS 以“Everybody needs good neighbours”为主题，用蓝色和格纹的组合打破黑白，试图探讨个人与环境之间的渗透与融合。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131123391GZFX5o3ul4kDmKH.png\" data-ratio=\"0.661321\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101311232439j0L7TMeNYJGckq.png\" data-ratio=\"1.497297\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112322lKAGb0TaOU9FipkJ.png\" data-ratio=\"1.479279\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112324MWkcT6jlv8iXJuxe.png\" data-ratio=\"1.486486\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112329ActuCrBiW4Ysk9JG.png\" data-ratio=\"1.495495\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112330SCV7XasyWnei5ghm.png\" data-ratio=\"1.491892\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112332KzwtfTEnYeIDOPh0.png\" data-ratio=\"1.495479\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112334Plc82Sq7gAzKfU1R.png\" data-ratio=\"1.485560\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112336F5fsVedI67S3vazB.png\" data-ratio=\"1.412297\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112337HOBKvZL9xFcC4YN7.png\" data-ratio=\"1.484740\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112339ZfpuSItUcWNC5Vrz.png\" data-ratio=\"1.486486\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112341yMHtUxhIP9Xa3vFJ.png\" data-ratio=\"1.484629\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112341v5BWlR0Zsu7LgJAV.png\" data-ratio=\"1.486438\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112342rh1ykXIvx0fdanLC.png\" data-ratio=\"1.491892\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112343ByqJ7RQUcNxiFZWH.png\" data-ratio=\"1.487410\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>SHUSHU/TONG 2018春夏系列用花朵和蝴蝶结元素延续了一直以来的少女感。灵感源自寺山修司1981年的电影《上海异人娼馆》， 在秀场中央构建了一个精致的东方客厅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112220no3PWHle9rKTJDXc.png\" data-ratio=\"0.609272\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112243q4yYJVeOTk9b3Pum.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112257uE9dGkSM5JBF6aWC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112219JqYMgBaZV7ifCNT8.png\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112219qa8wExNAKUBdo4Vs.png\" data-ratio=\"1.501075\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112221vD1tQm2yiKMghVON.png\" data-ratio=\"1.488372\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112221YzmyJaOXwV5BUWZi.png\" data-ratio=\"1.504292\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131122517B1XriuedUM4LVCw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112254VbdYRa4Gi1EeDSQP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112255YmMc7aXu8tLEyxDV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>设计师 Fiona 和 Kain 的品牌 FFIXXED STUDIOS 这次是本季 Presentation 首发，以日常穿着为基础，穿插透明面料拼接，悠闲简单。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112430vNJreck0uzfYgDIj.png\" data-ratio=\"1.406475\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112432yE41cMjKrgYCpvx5.png\" data-ratio=\"1.433692\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112435VEGaxhsCw0TlmDHd.png\" data-ratio=\"1.421622\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112439Wy7T86ojYLUhDE0F.png\" data-ratio=\"1.407942\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112444dB9OF3ukmtKjvYRT.png\" data-ratio=\"1.403226\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131124449mu87bWdwTxieJD4.png\" data-ratio=\"1.500907\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112445EwC74qV9WcZOk6I2.png\" data-ratio=\"1.405745\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131124468IfygsbSu7ajYKnz.png\" data-ratio=\"1.490090\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112451zAPEaUR1Gwr8dXKk.png\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112451x5gVY7lGANow9bM3.png\" data-ratio=\"1.414105\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112451pe5G9yHJ0knFmgfK.png\" data-ratio=\"1.413357\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112452BOi4qAVLzZUM1Ef2.png\" data-ratio=\"1.408602\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>新天地秀场上，没有太多惊喜。</p><p>C.J.YAO 带来了以“EAT”, “PLAY”, “LOL” 为主题，五颜六色的 2018 春夏系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112519H5TQpzcfXxVR3lod.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112526M6qzWGUvK48Q2kfc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131125272LIQJBK9RNbVzopr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112531ko6KauxfGSUJy2Mh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112531NloRCjvatUuh6bOY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112531lQY1TjeCbifrIOMJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112532FOqzgoXDIJjtQ5dV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131125333Oh0ql6L98c2FnHB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131125367T3w2AiQUNEOsplh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112540WBN3V7okfZ1luXqy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112542xNIHnsgBvQPLOlK1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112543cBuFx9ZJkegoqhwD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131125491OLpDtATQEJ3Vq4M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112550dH7ceiIv1q2lT8mJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112551EST0BMxrLq76Ne2b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112551a3PiqpjD6vnZXW2J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101311255183Ym4FNsP5yXJGkf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112613YlEbVaxPgh62HGAQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112614okWnc5UFTiwIHD1R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112614tROQD3ToIYJHclCi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112615dJ6MvnlU5bcYygew.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>设计师王长荣的同名品牌 WANG CHANGRONG 于 2016 年创立于深圳。本季女装系列的主题是“Ocean Flame”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131127044eRvEtYxapd8F19W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131127077iMrkcJXLVY2fSxw.jp