> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131127383d9zlrfwNohBsXS1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112740tKWXg0muTYf37JHs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112741M7Srnxo6YVZk3DAK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>设计师俞用雷以《雪国列车》为主题，打造了品牌 KRBL 差异化形态的单品和造型。本季的男装系列分为三个部分：幸存者、统治者和通灵者。分别以结实耐用的蓝色调，象征冷酷麻木的绿色调，以及代表神秘探索欲的白色和卡其色诠释。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112821OWrzZl97IeiPwFMQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112844pNz82ZV6SBLyMr3D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112848N1xOLZKMw2ehHVXk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112855CopLSG5Aga6bmy91.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131128197TvKPFCjVswB9kml.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112826LExTvSZ9cisBuj2t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112827W4tc9H2oEfpjmeaT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112829lAHmYyuBs6O1bVWx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171013112832hIN0zgfdYR3ojWtS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710131128329EH5elhO1UFkSiCa.jpg\" data-